title: xReign of Terrorx - There's a Last Time For Everything
description:
Concious, straight edge rap by Dirt-E Chris former guitarist of straight edge, hardcore band xBishopx. xReign of Terrorx started out as a non-serious project with more people involved, but over the years has willowed down to just Chris and has a serious, sometimes positive, sometimes negative message about the world we live in and the things we face day-by-day. say word.
